Author: cummo22
Text: Precisely. I can eat a kilo of peanut butter for breakfast, but I can also fast for 7 days. There is no middle ground.

Author: onIytoldthemoon
Text: I prefer fasting over restricting as well. I have this "all or nothing" mentality for some reason, so if I eat as much as a grape, I go full-bingeing mode.
